// ============================================================================
// VALIDATION RULES (enforced at application layer)
// ============================================================================
// - command: Must be one of ['specify', 'plan', 'task', 'implement', 'clarify']
// - status transitions: pending → running → (completed | failed)
// - completedAt: Must be null when status is pending or running
// - completedAt: Required when status is completed or failed
// - branch: Max 200 characters (Git branch name length limit)
// - commitSha: Max 40 characters (SHA-1 hash length)
// - logs: Unlimited length (PostgreSQL TEXT supports up to 1GB)

